    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2013-06-28</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2013-11-01T14:53:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Passenger Safety and Security Act or the PASS Act - Amends the federal judicial code to include state and local agencies among institutions with which the Attorney General shall exchange identification records and information, including agencies acting through a qualified transportation regulation association to conduct criminal background investigations as a condition of issuing a taxi, chauffeur, public passenger, or other similar license.</p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>PASS Act</title>
